  "description": "<p>•\tReport creation and validation with stakeholders</p><p>•\tSet up, organise and maintain tools, templates and SharePoint content</p><p>•\tMailbox administration and management</p><p>•\tAccess management and data reconciliation</p><p>•\tMaintenance and execution of regular and ad hoc tasks for Workday, PPM, PEMS and SAP systems</p><p>•\tProficient in MS Excel, Visio, Word and PowerPoint</p><p>•\tOffice administration duties</p><p>•\tAble to manage tasks end to end independently</p><p>•\tData entry and system based data validation</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
